Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.07,0:40:46.17,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Stood in the way.\N{\rChinese}好的？站在路上。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.89,0:40:50.03,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? They basically sacrificed themselves so the other army,\N{\rChinese}好的，...??…??????????????????????????????????????????????????????…??…??…??…??…??…???
