Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.65,0:45:06.81,English,,0,0,0,,Right? So I don't think it's Persia.\N{\rChinese}??
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.97,0:45:09.07,English,,0,0,0,,I think most people agree it was not Persia.\N{\rChinese}我想我方块??
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.15,0:45:13.61,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Second possibility is it was personal.\N{\rChinese}好的？第二个可能是它是个人的。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.23,0:45:17.49,English,,0,0,0,,And that's kind of strange.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.71,0:45:19.01,English,,0,0,0,,Right? Because Philip,\N{\rChinese}Right? Because Philip,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.21,0:45:23.17,English,,0,0,0,,he's very good at inspiring loyalty from others.\N{\rChinese}他很擅长激发他人忠诚。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.29,0:45:25.73,English,,0,0,0,,He's also good at reading people. Right?\N{\rChinese}他也很擅长读人。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.53,0:45:30.25,English,,0,0,0,,So I don't think it was personal.\N{\rChinese}所以我认为不是个人原因。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.03,0:45:32.89,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, it could be, but I don't think it is.\N{\rChinese}我想它可以是也可...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.99,0:45:37.51,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And this leaves us with the possibility of Olympias and Alexander.\N{\rChinese}好的，先说动机吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.51,0:45:40.95,English,,0,0,0,,And here, it makes sense because\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.95,0:45:43.45,English,,0,0,0,,they both have both the motive and the opportunity.\N{\rChinese}他们都有动机与机会。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.75,0:45:45.19,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So let me first explain motive.\N{\rChinese}好的，先说动机吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.49,0:45:48.07,English,,0,0,0,,The motive is very easy to understand.\N{\rChinese}动机很容易理解。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.65,0:45:54.19,English,,0,0,0,,If Philip were to die, Alexander would become king.\N{\rChinese}如果菲利普去世，亚历山大将成为国王。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.39,0:45:55.59,English,,0,0,0,,Right? And\N{\rChinese}右？然后
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.59,0:45:59.55,English,,0,0,0,,this is at the height of the glory of Macedon.\N{\rChinese}右边? 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.71,0:46:01.29,English,,0,0,0,,They have the world's greatest military.\N{\rChinese}他们拥有世界最强的军队。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.29,0:46:03.25,English,,0,0,0,,They conquered all of Greece.\N{\rChinese}他们征服了全部希腊。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.05,0:46:06.37,English,,0,0,0,,Persia is an easy target.\N{\rChinese}波斯是易攻之地。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.61,0:46:09.45,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And maybe they were afraid that\N{\rChinese}好的？也许他们害怕菲利普去波斯，太迟了。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.45,0:46:11.75,English,,0,0,0,,if Philip goes to Persia, it would be too late.\N{\rChinese}如果菲利普去到波斯，若是个好时机？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.71,0:46:17.79,English,,0,0,0,,The other problem is Philip is an excellent judge of character.\N{\rChinese}先前……………??
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.31,0:46:20.45,English,,0,0,0,,And what's clear about Alexander,\N{\rChinese}和……？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.83,0:46:22.77,English,,0,0,0,,from a very early age,\N{\rChinese}从………
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.13,0:46:25.57,English,,0,0,0,,is he was a very violent young man.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.83,0:46:27.81,English,,0,0,0,,He couldn't really control his emotions.\N{\rChinese}他确实没能把握住自己的情绪。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.31,0:46:29.61,English,,0,0,0,,You have Philip, right?\N{\rChinese}你们有菲利普吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.79,0:46:31.27,English,,0,0,0,,You're kind of like, I don't know.\N{\rChinese}你们好像……
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.27,0:46:33.83,English,,0,0,0,,Do I really want this guy to be the heir to my empire?\N{\rChinese}我真的想让他继承我的帝国吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.27,0:46:35.69,English,,0,0,0,,Could he manage the empire?\N{\rChinese}他能管理好帝国吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.35,0:46:37.95,English,,0,0,0,,Plus, remember, Philip has a lot of wives, right?\N{\rChinese}再加上，菲利普有多位妻子，才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.29,0:46:40.77,English,,0,0,0,,So over time, he could have new sons.\N{\rChinese}在此时，...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.85,0:46:44.23,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Does that make sense?\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.43,0:46:45.91,English,,0,0,0,,So the motive is very clear.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.61,0:46:50.25,English,,0,0,0,,And the opportunity makes sense because they're all one family, right?\N{\rChinese}和机会相符，因为他们全是同一家，才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.41,0:46:54.27,English,,0,0,0,,The bodyguard is in constant communication with Olympias.\N{\rChinese}保镶在与奥利米亚斯的沟通中。
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.71,0:46:56.83,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And what gives evidence?\N{\rChinese}好的，...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.51,0:47:01.89,English,,0,0,0,,What provides evidence for this? So what we're trying to do is,\N{\rChinese}什么提供了证据？我们要做的就是，
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.15,0:47:07.29,English,,0,0,0,,after the death of Philip's bodyguard named Pausanias,\N{\rChinese}在此后，帕乌萨尼亚斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.51,0:47:12.01,English,,0,0,0,,Olympias actually made a monument to him.\N{\rChinese}在此后…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.29,0:47:16.13,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And\N{\rChinese}...
