Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.31,0:47:28.81,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Maybe he didn't participate in the killing of his father,\N{\rChinese}好吧，回到…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.87,0:47:33.25,English,,0,0,0,,in the plotting. Of the assassination.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.21,0:47:36.19,English,,0,0,0,,But he clearly wanted his father dead.\N{\rChinese}但他明显想让父亲去世。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.69,0:47:40.13,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And next class, we will discuss this.\N{\rChinese}好的，下一节课我们会讨论这个。
